{{Quote|Crans, Portin &ndash; go get in the passageway. If I whistle, come out and kill everything that's not us.|[[Zothip]]|<ref name="Vision of the Future">''[[Vision of the Future]]''</ref>}}
'''Portin''' was one of the [[Cavrilhu Pirates]] under the command of the pirate leader [[Zothip]].

Portin, Zothip, and several other pirates including [[Crans]], [[Grinner]], and [[Control (individual)|Control]], sneaked into Moff [[Vilim Disra|Disra's]] quarters on the Imperial Capital of [[Bastion/Legends|Bastion]]. Portin didn't realize that they were being followed by the Mystryl Shadow Guard known as [[Karoly D'ulin]]. Once inside, Karoly killed Zothip. After Zothip's death, Control took over as the head of the Cavrilhu Pirates.

